title: Champion Weekly Rotation Wont Work??
body:
I recently just started a new account and the weekly champion rotation is still stuck on the same champions as last week? When i play the game other players are able to select the new champions but i cant?? 

Help me!

replies.body:
How odd. Could you provide a time-stamped screen-shot of this?

Not that I can actually do anything about it. You'd probably have to make a [support ticket](https://support.leagueoflegends.com/anonymous_requests/new) to correct server-side errors.
